flowRoot.flowPara: On Friday evening, we'll have a Barbecue just outside building B, featuring proper German beer from Karlsruhe's Vogelbru brewery and regional barbecue artist Dennis Ludwig with his XXL smoker. Drinks from 19:00, food from 20:00.
Mixed vegetables with Ludwig-Grill smoked salt
Cous cous salad w/ fresh herbs
Low & Slow cooked pork neck on a smoker grill seasoned with Ludwig-Grill BBQ spices and a Maple-Chipotle BBQ Sauce.
Homemade raspberry ice cream with chocolate chips
Smoked salmon with a Rosemary and Lemon Sauce.
